          <title>Robby Ashford leads Wake Forest past Mississippi State 43-29 in Duke's Mayo Bowl</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Robby Ashford threw for 303 yards and three touchdowns and ran for 50 yards and two scores, Koredell Bartley scored on a 100-yard kickoff return and Wake Forest beat Mississippi State 43-29 in the Duke’s Mayo Bowl on Friday night, earning coach Jake Dickert a mayonnaise bath.]]></description>
